questions.quote: Oh, you're not gonna believe what happened to me today! Ralph Lauren called, and gave me my job back!
No. No, see when I first meet somebody it's uh it's mostly panic, anxiety, and a great deal of sweating.
Joey, come on! It doesn't matter, you know, it's not like anything's gonna happen.
Look, there's Chandler. You knew, that stupid friend of Ross'. Said I'm fat. You know I've already lost 4 pounds!
Oh...Joey, you bummed him out! This was the happiest dog in the world, and he spends half a day with you, and look at him!
And when I told her that I was gonna be moving in with Chandler, she was really supportive. You were so great. You made it so easy. And now you have to leave. And I have to live with a boy!!
Now sweetie, I know you don't like my office parties, but you can wear your new boots. See? Every cloud has a...supple leather lining.
I guess you can get back to deciding on what to get me for a present!
Whatever I decide to do, I'm gonna be starting a career from scratch. It's gonna be a while before I make a living at it. Maybe now is not the right time to be starting a family.
Oh, no, no, I don't have one. I just need to talk to my friend.
